libbgcode: libbgcode (library for the binary G-code format)
libbgcode:
libbgcode: LibBGCode implements PrusaSlicer's binary G-code (.bgcode) file
libbgcode: format: a block-structured container with separate blocks for
libbgcode: metadata and G-code, with optional compression (heatshrink and
libbgcode: zlib) plus MeatPack encoding. It provides binarize and convert
libbgcode: components and a bgcode command line tool.
libbgcode:
libbgcode: It is used by PrusaSlicer and PrusaSlicer-based applications.
libbgcode:
libbgcode: Homepage: https://github.com/prusa3d/libbgcode
